# AVD-DS-0002: "Image user should not be root."
# Intentional: the entrypoint (docker/entrypoint.sh) MUST start as root to chown
# the bind-mounted /data and /media to PUID:PGID for Unraid, then drops privileges
# via su-exec before running the app. The container does not run the app as root.
AVD-DS-0002
DS002
